message.content: cs.IT, cs.IT is the most likely category as the paper deals with information theory and channel resolvability. Other likely categories could be cs.DS (data structures and algorithms) as the paper involves developing bounds and studying convergence, cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper deals with approximation and convergence, cs.CR (cryptography and security) as the paper applies the results to the wiretap channel problem, and cs.SI (social and information networks) as the paper deals with mutual covering lemma.
